data.description:
Charming bungalow, set on a corner lot, located only steps away from Lakeside Park 1, or walk to the Marina at Ortega Landing!  Hardwood oak floors, vinyl plank flooring in updated kitchen and bath. Updated lighting and plumbing fixtures. Exterior has vinyl siding for easy maintenance. Detached 2 car garage w/electric could be a workshop!  HVAC 2019. Roof 2019. Relax on your front porch and enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage.  Walk/bike to the shops & restaurants of Ortega Park AND only 1.3 miles to the shops & restaurants of Avondale! Minutes away from NAS.
*ASSUMABLE 3.125% VA LOAN AVAILABLE TO QUALIFIED VA BUYERS*
